                        "__typename": "EmployerReviewRG",
                        "advice": "The company is doing well and staff work hard. EF is a fun place to work but the fact we get paid so little (especially for a skilled job - teachers have to be qualified), really puts a downer on the experience and makes us feel undervalued and like you're cutting corners. Also - pay the host families more.",
