                                "languageId": "eng",
                                "originalLanguageId": null,
                                "response": "Thanks for taking the time to share your experience with us. We take pride in helping to bring new teachers to China and setting them up for success in their careers. We are so glad you enjoyed working with your students and the international experience of working with people from all over the world. We are sorry to hear that you did not feel that there were enough opportunities for travel. We understand how hard teachers work and are constantly looking for ways to promote and support a healthy work-life balance. For example, we try to give our teachers the opportunity to attend sponsored social and cultural events and provide a number of development opportunities and programs to assist with many of the daily challenges of teaching. In April and May we are sponsoring a health fair in our major cities with a focus on physical and mental health. These are just some examples of initiaitves to promote a balanced and healthy lifestyle for our teachers. We take any allegations of discrimination very seriously. Please contact us at compliance.china@ef.com so that we can conduct a thorough and fair investigation.",
